    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "TWA\nN902TW\nTRANS WORLD\n00080000",
      "TWA-TRANS WORLD AIRLINES\nMcDonnell Douglas Super 80\nThe economical and fuel-efficient Super 80 joined TWA's\nfleet in the Spring of 1983, bringing with it proven passenger\npopularity,\nalong\nwith\nnew,\nquiet\nPratt\n\u0026 Whitney\nJT8D-217A engines, each producing 20,000 pounds of\nthrust.\nPublished by Aviation World, Inc., P.O. Box 188, Bethel, Conn. 06801 U.S.A.\nD- 042\n84599-D\npost card\nPhoto courtesy Trans World Airlines\nN902TW c/n 49153\n2002.113.485"
    ],
